<section class="career text-center">
  <h2>The Icalier Career Path</h2>
  <p>If you're a hacker by nature, you have a passion for making delightful digital products, then you sound like a person we'd like to work with. </p>
  <br />
  <p>You will join a family of young, talented, individuals striving to make an impact.  </p>
  <p>At Icalia, you'll get paid to give a shit. </p>
</section>
<section class="perks text-center">
  <div class="container">
    <h4 class="title-section-perks">Perks for the team</h4>
    <p class="section-description">We care about our team and culture. Asside from the basics, you'll instantly be on a path of becoming a better Hacker, Designer, Business Person. </p>
    <div class="row clearfix">

      <div class="perk col-3 square-bg-1 ">
        <figure>
          <%= image_tag "perk1.png", class: "perk-icon" %>
          <figcaption>
          <h3 class="perk-title">Training</h3>
          <p class="perk-description">Leverage our collective knowledge, through constant training.</p>
          </figcaption>
        </figure>
      </div>

      <div class="perk col-3 square-bg-2">
        <figure>
          <%= image_tag "perk2.png", class: "perk-icon" %>
          <figcaption>
          <h3 class="perk-title">Medical insurance</h3>
          <p class="perk-description">Besides the basic insurance for full-time memebers, we offer an additional medical insurance to guarantee your tranquility when something happens.</p>
          </figcaption>
        </figure>
      </div>

      <div class="perk col-6 square-bg-3">
        <figure>
          <%= image_tag "perk3.png", class: "perk-icon" %>
          <figcaption>
          <h3 class="perk-title">Your launch pad</h3>
          <p class="perk-description">Take advantage of a great team and share with anyone your idea. You can build something great with all the talent available, and maybe start the next great thing. </p>
          </figcaption>
        </figure>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row clearfix">
      <div class="perk col-6 square-bg-3">
        <figure>
          <%= image_tag "perk4.png", class: "perk-icon" %>
          <figcaption>
          <h3 class="perk-title">Creative Time</h3>
          <p class="perk-description">As technology advances and changes, we need to be up to date every single day. Creative Time allows team members to spend 20% of their time on something not-client related.</p>
          </figcaption>
        </figure>
      </div>

      <div class="perk col-3 square-bg-1">
        <figure>
          <%= image_tag "perk5.png", class: "perk-icon" %>
          <figcaption>
          <h3 class="perk-title">Remote work</h3>
          <p class="perk-description">Sometimes inspiration is outside the building. Work from home or your favorite coffeeshop. </p>
          </figcaption>
        </figure>
      </div>

      <div class="perk col-3 square-bg-2">
        <figure>
          <%= image_tag "perk6.png", class: "perk-icon" %>
          <figcaption>
          <h3 class="perk-title">Online certifications</h3>
          <p class="perk-description">If you want to take your newly acquired knowledge to the next level, we can sponsor your certification in any MOOC or platform available. </p>
          </figcaption>
        </figure>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

